// HOW TO
1) copy and paste the code above into the HTML of the page that you want the image on
2) Put the image link into the quotation marks after the href attribute and the img src attribute
3) type the needed information into the add a description of the image here such as genus, species, geolocation, etc
4) type a simple description of the image into the quotation marks after the alt term
5) you should be good after this, repeat for every image
